{"tid":1474480,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能解放軍黎香港玩「清君側」隊冧晒班警察？","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T08:29:57.000Z","uid":263448,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d99e07933ff06e1e6549e5b9e0f0f681b4102dc6","tid":1474480,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:50:07.000Z","msg":"依家隱約feel到黎緊示威好似會以和平為主，少對峙咁。<br />\n818絕對要大力宣傳係和平為主導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反觀警察呢堆瘋狗，無論場風波贏定係輸，都必然係被清算既一群。<br />\n警察形象已經係721跌到谷底，8月份仲要限制解放，催淚彈放題，開埋陰陽眼，本來為咗製造混亂，嫁禍比示威者帶來麻煩，但都依然舉步維艱。<br />\n<br />\n新政府無論係小圈子定民選特首，都必然要面對警隊形象底落既問題。<br />\n（當然，如果係由小圈子選舉，分分鐘清算完警察，就用「缺乏警力」為由，引入大量公安。）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但今次風波，揭發咗懷疑有武警、公安、解放軍介入，即使要清算，都可能會接觸到呢個問題，呢個亦係麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n假如黎緊示威者都有默契地，唔衝突，唔升級武力，甚至溫和地阻止內鬼製造混亂，友善對待藍絲反對派製造麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n咁就連殺警戲都難拍。<br />\n<br />\n所以我大膽推斷，由「曱甴」去人化開始，潛移默化緊班毅進傻仔放下罪惡感（依家爆頭見埋血都仲敢話係英雄），某日會因小事而發瘋，開實彈殺死示威者。<br />\n<br />\n然後中共就話警察失控，屠殺和平示威者，中央對港警失去信心，緊急調派解放軍，解救香港民眾，堅決支持香港和平穩定，維護一國兩制，乜乜柒柒。<br />\n<br />\n果頭講完10分鐘到港，佔領各區警署，屠番幾千個警察，燒埋一啲&quot;重要資料&quot;，放低啲假資料。<br />\n<br />\n搞咗大半日，清算埋林鄭，林鄭上台道歉下台。<br />\n<br />\n事後，中共發文章，將所以責任交比林鄭，事件定性為警察暴動，林鄭放縱警察，屠殺中國人，中共心痛港人，調派解放軍解救香港。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，因為暴警已經死晒，資料不全，難以追究真相。<br />\n<br />\n臨時特首重新展開官民對話。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是次事件為.......事件..."},{"pid":"56ad72ae25d79e7030ef47a73cac186766f0e63f","tid":1474480,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81c57ab2eb6cf06ea664b4a9d55b44eb20852fd1","tid":1474480,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:51:45.000Z","msg":"共產黨點會虧待佢條狗，睇下劉江華就知"},{"pid":"b05dcdf00cf3a8b6e109d4072608f6797455dd3a","tid":1474480,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:54:29.000Z","msg":"ummm..<br />\n<br />\n人地有2/3人唔喺警署放咗工"},{"pid":"d710e31073f2a315dec28efcf627017c3e16480f","tid":1474480,"uid":172627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:50.000Z","msg":"難，因為全國撐警，你一死，<br />\n<br />\n全國會點諗"},{"pid":"977ac81ac42e63251d9697b3d01853bf48b99e4e","tid":1474480,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05dcdf00cf3a8b6e109d4072608f6797455dd3a","tid":1474480,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:54:29.000Z","msg